reviewText: I love it as much as volumes 1-2! They ended this series way too early - this could have gone on for at least 70 edisodes...so many places they could have taken our young characters.

The video quality is not great, the audio only average and  the Navigation/chapters not fabulous. Story line is ok.

Not terrible, not expensive but not a wonderful way to spend a couple of hours.

Great costumes. The witches curse was a surprising twist to the story.
I recommed for those who likre twisted story lines
this show rocks and i've watched it over and over and i'm glad i bought it and it rocks thanks
